title: Bug 114470[Smoke]Error message throws when using new Date('3/2/2005') as value in table filter.
OB: When using the value new Date('3/2/2005') in a table filter, an error message is thrown.
EB: No error message should be thrown when using the value new Date('3/2/2005') in a table filter.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open the table filter.
2. Enter the value new Date('3/2/2005').
3. Apply the filter and observe if an error message is thrown.
